<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2645> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2645" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Brought the fleet to Cephallenia (Liv. 42.35.3, and 48.5; cf. Polyb. 27.7.1), then sending it under his brother to Chalcis he took over from Lentulus the siege of Haliartus in Boeotia (Liv. 42.56.1-7), which he captured and enslaved (42.63.3-11). Thisbe then surrendered and was placed under Roman partizans while the pro-Macedonians were sold into slavery (42.63.3-12; cf. Polyb. 27.5.3; SIG\n     646). Cf. I. de Délos 460 E, 19.{417}" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2643> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2643" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Election Liv. 42.28.5 Provinces and armies 42.31.6-9." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2438> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2438" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Province: from the promontory of Minerva around to Barium (Liv. 40.18.7-8, and 26.8). Cf. Grueber, CRRBM 1.396f.; Cesano, Stud. Num. 1.197f." .
